>> 0xFF ¶

>> "--- Booleans ---" ¶

>> #1 ¶
>> #0 ¶
cmp_gt = (𑋱𑋲 > 𑋴)
cmp_lt = (𑋴 > 𑋱𑋲)
>> cmp_gt ¶
>> cmp_lt ¶
>> #𑋱 ¶
>> #𑋰 ¶

